Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:05.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看我不是究极女仆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.69,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(955.2,923.8)}托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.69,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs110\bord8\3c&H9D00EB&\4c&HA51DC4&\pos(1012.8,151)}女          仆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然不是  又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:11.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没什么  虽然我也觉得自己已经登峰造极了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我找到了这本书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,女仆咖啡厅新开张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还挺近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:21.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里写着「最出色的女仆迎接您的光临」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敢自称最出色的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竟然无视我的存在  进行这种夸大宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,夸大宣传可不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我眼前的这条龙就在做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.18,Kobayashi S2 - Comment Down,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\fs100\bord5\pos(963.2,796.4)}其实是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:39.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之先用诅咒之炎把她们烧成寸草不生的暗黑尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正可谓是又燃又萌？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.68,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：日语中“燃”和“萌”谐音。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  绝对不准这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:48.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之我先去侦察敌情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:58.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你没惹什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要在那里工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:01.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.95,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\bord2\pos(790.666,650)}因为我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.96,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs130\bord2\pos(1103.066,902.133)}小林家的龙女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我当时意志高昂地冲进敌人的伏魔殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还伏魔殿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是来面试兼职的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,穿着女仆装来的  看来是志在必得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我败给了你的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,录取了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是这样  我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那间女仆咖啡厅没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,反正最近小林和康娜都不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我无事可做很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是闲来无事去打工的家庭主妇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你是真要去打工啊  没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:15.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是每天都像这样做着女仆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经驾轻就熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我现在是在公司上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:24.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是在老家时是在餐饮店工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听好了  不可以小看服务业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然女仆咖啡厅的cosplay女仆形式不符合我的价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是她们的服务精神值得我尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是个好机会  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就去学学什么叫服务业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都有点害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从那之后已经有段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔有好好工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,小林太爱操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\3c&HB976F6&\pos(962,868.333)}康娜卡姆依
