Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以及大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多和托尔大人一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看来是间很朴实的女仆咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然现在已经不怎么讲萌这种词了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但这里还保留了那个时代的遗风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看看菜单是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还是挺忠实还原基础的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,每样菜式有对应的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大概像「变好吃吧  萌萌心动」这类的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也会各有不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林好懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这件事我只告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我以前有想过来这种店里打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,结果失败了  失败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我不是很懂  但是同情你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比起这些  托尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,10号桌的料理做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,盘子不够了  快补上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:52.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厉害的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是厨师长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了  厨师长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔厨师长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了大家工作效率这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是来看我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是做得挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让我吃了一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对我而言就是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样的话在女仆之路上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,女仆…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这根本不是女仆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去拜托看看能不能换去大堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  我觉得这里很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,火山龙才适合这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你重新进一次店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,变好喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,啧  该叫主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,厨师长当时换来大堂的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说是不想称呼小林以外的人为主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不对  她也从来没有叫过我主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请在这边坐下稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  终于可以点单了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蛋包饭  蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  两份蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就让我来施展让蛋包饭变好吃的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可爱一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,献予统治世界的影之王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以外法将此成就至高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,祈愿丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,礼赞富足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,改换价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,献出石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吾之魔将化作泥沼播撒污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吾之理将侵蚀理性使人癫狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真实虚幻  交织变换
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,变好吃吧  萌萌心动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  已经变好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:57.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是魔法是诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把厨师长给我叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:09.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,厨师长  女仆  龙  都是我托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至少能力还是有的  仅限能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我还是不想当小林以外的人的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不能走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:29.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,厨师长做的料理已经是我们店的招牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,网上也已经有很多相关的评论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,厨师长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个  既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就教你们让料理变好吃的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:41.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类施法的话  要先画出魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是间好店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么我要两份蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我要施展变好吃的魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.04,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,献予统治世界的影之王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这间女仆咖啡厅还真是别具一格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.00,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,以外法将此成就至高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.84,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,祈愿丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.48,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\frz9.504\fs100\b1\pos(946,780)}蛋包饭很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.02,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,780)\frz348.3}料理很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(956,838)}蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是料理啊  女仆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对我作为女仆的评价呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别弄坏鼠标哦
Comment: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第1话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.99,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur10\bord1.5\pos(971.467,594.467)}新来的龙、伊露露！（再次请多关照）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以预见接下来的天气会急剧变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请随时关注后续的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今日凌晨发生了一起大型山体滑坡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:54.63,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,塌方处仿佛是被人为地削去一般  存在诸多疑点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是我和托尔相遇的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然对我们的纪念之地做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要找出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,送他进去欣嫩谷  或者叫晢罕南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：欣嫩谷，是耶路撒冷原本作为垃圾场和乱葬岗使用的一个谷地，希伯来圣经中提及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(88,61)}犹大诸王在此处以火牺牲自己孩子，后成为炼狱的代名词。伊斯兰教中将类似的概念称为晢罕南。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最后喂给阿米特吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.64,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：阿穆特，古埃及神话中鳄头、狮上身、河马下身的生物，死后审判中被认定的恶人会被它吞下，永远不能安息。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过能做到这种事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那个时间我在复习游戏活动要用到的打call和口号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,868.333)\3c&H953F3E&\fad(700,0)}法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\3c&H953F3E&}（其实是龙）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚昨天在国外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我们的魔力是连接在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她在哪里我都能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.79,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,鲷鱼烧  真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.33,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(964,874)\3c&HED5C2A&}艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.33,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&HED5C2A&}（其实是龙）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你突然干什么啊  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,犯人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛  今天新闻报道说有座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对了  我也很在意那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也不是艾尔玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还以为是托尔做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就是说不是我们认识的龙做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能破坏我的结界的龙很少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.04,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(972.8,893.4)\3c&H9C48F1&}伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:08.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很美丽的街景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢笑着的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在这里就能尽情地享受破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是混沌之龙却在和人类一同嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有点兴趣  所以稍微观察了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是已经看腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,简单来说  你是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:42.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,属于混沌势力中最偏激的派系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她很享受破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定是跟着托尔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.84,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\bord4\b0\pos(968.667,848.333)}自己就是跟着托尔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:54.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用说  那家伙肯定是想毁灭这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:57.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是  托尔肯定有办法解决的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  伊露露只比托尔稍弱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是她们的战斗会把这一带都破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,关于这点  她也会想办法解决的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你相信托尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:11.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毕竟我能做的也只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我当然要相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不准在这个世界搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,瞎说什么  我可是混沌势力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做不到就揍你一顿然后送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要打架可是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种程度的攻击对我可没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好  目标是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是陷入苦战了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔要一边保护城市一边战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,处境非常不利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛不去帮她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是调和势力  按理说跟托尔是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我展开了驱散人类的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但那只是为了避免麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其他的龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫纳阁下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,估计会说「自己的屁股自己去擦」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚阁下是旁观势力  所以不会出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至于康纳则力量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔被打败的话  我就去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会保护好小林以及这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那托尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我嘴上说着相信托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但这并不能帮助到托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟无动于衷没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但除此之外  我也只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  你要我去帮托尔是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:48.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等  再怎么说也别想用这个收买我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:53.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖啡冻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,枫糖浆松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想吃多少甜品都买给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我打中了30发炎酸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爪击也有重击了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就说一句「好痛」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这可难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想不到该怎么杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,全力攻击的话会毁坏城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但不这样做的话  就无法打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对于你的攻击  我也快忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但又必须保护城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我快炸裂了  不如干脆毁灭一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛展开屏障了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不过是和小林做了份交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和人类打成一片  让我感到恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,接下来我要动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以我真正的形态毁灭这整个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差点没控制住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然受到的伤害并没那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我却差点忘记自己要保护这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,甚至一度觉得除了小林之外的人小林以外的人死了也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样的话就不能再待在这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无论多艰难我都能努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要为了能留在小林身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,任何艰难险阻都拦不住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说服了艾尔玛出手帮助托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我一直被教导说人类是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:46.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.52,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\3c&HD25090&\pos(965.6,865.8)}露科亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.52,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD25090&\fad(600,0)}（其实是龙）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.02,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,「是我」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.44,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:03.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,电车？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,背包？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赔偿  今天之内  200万？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是有点棘手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,光是打开传送门就累死个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真亏托尔能把这么费劲的事情做得易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赶末班车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不让托尔来接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名为小林的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么你能和龙生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我并没有做过什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而是托尔主动迎合我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不恐惧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感到恐惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:07.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毕竟这么可爱  有什么怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你对她发情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你迷上了化身成人类形态的托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以才不怕她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是不是  瞎说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,强烈地否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:22.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这什么鬼  好夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:32.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你终究不过是个人类  违抗不了欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  将你那下流的男人本性暴露无遗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很想沉溺在这温柔乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,仅限此刻我允许你对我发泄欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:46.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.34,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,每天我见到那两坨巨大的脂肪块就又气又恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赶不上末班车了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,车门关闭  请勿靠近车门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还没闹够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我无法认同你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龙与人类不可能共存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,两者共处就会因各自差异而感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直痛苦下去  乃至将憎恨上升至种族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:40.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尊敬转化成嫉妒  早晚产生裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔对你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过是稀奇感罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等她对你失去兴趣  终有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没事  听着呢听着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之就是什么种族差异之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不认可我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你还要说服我这种人干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要你纠正自己的认知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么就让我借用你刚才的话来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们因各自差异而感到快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直快乐下去  乃至将喜爱上升至种族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尊敬转化成信赖  早晚产生牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我从和托尔的生活里感受到的就是这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这不过是诡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,实际上很可能酿成悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这不过是在用漂亮的话语敷衍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们会争吵  也产生过裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但对此视而不见  产生负面情绪也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,即便不能正确理解对方的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但也会用自己的方式尝试配合彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总能凑合着生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是人类的思维方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  是小林我个人的思维方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:06.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你没有把龙的思维方式和伊露露的思维方式区分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:09.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没必要区分  都是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:10.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么决定「龙的思维方式」的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,并不是伊露露这条龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说得再天花乱坠  也不过是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你身为女人  所以才不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露是离开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是什么
