Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类灭亡的危机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.42,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fad(0,300)\pos(968,661.933)}下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:28.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林和我两人的爱情故事又开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:30.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然出现了新的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:31.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经不会再出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啊
Comment: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第二话
